{# templates/roadmaps/personal-finance/how-to-negotiate-bills.html.twig #}
{% extends 'base-roadmaps.html.twig' %}

    {% block stylesheets %}
        {{ parent() }}
        {{ encore_entry_link_tags('personal_finance_css') }}
    {% endblock %}

    {% block javascripts %}
        {{ parent() }}
        {{ encore_entry_script_tags('personal_finance_js') }}
    {% endblock %}

{% block body %}
    <div class="container">
        <!-- article hero -->
        <div class="article-hero animate">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <div class="hero-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-comment-dots"></i>
                </div>
                <h1>How to Negotiate Bills <span>& Lower Monthly Costs</span></h1>
                <p class="hero-description">
                    💬 Did you know that a single 10‑minute phone call can save you $300+ a year? Most companies have unadvertised discounts just for asking. This guide gives you word‑for‑word scripts and the best timing to lower your internet, phone, cable, and subscription bills.
                </p>
                <div class="phase-tag">
                    <i class="fas fa-flag-checkered"></i> PHASE 3 · PRACTICAL EXECUTION · 7 min read
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- table of contents (interactive) -->
        <div class="toc">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-list-ul" style="color: var(--personal-color);"></i> What you'll learn (click to jump)</h3>
            <div class="toc-grid">
                <a href="#why-negotiate"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Why negotiation works</a>
                <a href="#mindset"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Mindset & preparation</a>
                <a href="#scripts"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Proven scripts</a>
                <a href="#internet-cable"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Internet & cable</a>
                <a href="#phone"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Phone & wireless</a>
                <a href="#subscriptions"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Subscriptions & memberships</a>
                <a href="#timing"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Best time to call</a>
                <a href="#apps"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Apps & tools</a>
                <a href="#cheat-sheet"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Cheat sheet</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- content starts -->
        <h2 id="why-negotiate"><i class="fas fa-hand-holding-usd"></i> Why negotiation works (even for introverts)</h2>
        <p>Companies count on you not asking. Retention departments have budgets to keep you – they can offer discounts, waive fees, or upgrade services. A 2022 survey found that <strong>74% of people who asked for a better deal got one</strong>. The average annual saving: $320.</p>
        <div class="highlight-box">
            <strong><i class="fas fa-bolt"></i> Key insight:</strong> You’re not being “pushy.” You’re a loyal customer asking for a fair price. Most reps are empowered to help if you’re polite and persistent.
        </div>

        <h2 id="mindset"><i class="fas fa-brain"></i> Mindset & preparation</h2>
        <p>Before you dial, gather your weapons:</p>
        <ul class="checklist">
            <li><i class="fas fa-file-invoice"></i> Your latest bill (know what you pay).</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-tag"></i> Competitor offers – check websites for new‑customer deals.</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-phone"></i> A calm hour when you won’t be rushed.</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-smile"></i> Friendly, respectful attitude (reps respond to kindness).</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="pro-tip">
            <i class="fas fa-microphone"></i> <strong>Pro tip:</strong> Smile while you talk – it changes your tone and makes you sound warmer.
        </div>

        <h2 id="scripts"><i class="fas fa-comment-dots"></i> Proven scripts for any bill</h2>
        <p>Use these templates and adapt them to your situation.</p>

        <div class="script-box">
            <i class="fas fa-quote-left"></i> <strong>General opener:</strong><br>
            “Hi, I’m reviewing my bill and noticed the price has gone up. I’ve been a loyal customer for [X] years, but I’m seeing offers from [competitor] for $[amount] less. Is there any discount or promotion you can apply to keep my business?”
        </div>
        <div class="script-box">
            <i class="fas fa-quote-left"></i> <strong>If they say no:</strong><br>
            “I understand. Could you check if there are any unadvertised loyalty discounts, or perhaps waive the [fee/equipment charge]? I’d really like to stay with you.”
        </div>
        <div class="script-box">
            <i class="fas fa-quote-left"></i> <strong>If they transfer you to retention:</strong><br>
            “I was thinking of switching because of the price. What can you do to make it worth my while to stay?”
        </div>

        <h2 id="internet-cable"><i class="fas fa-wifi"></i> Negotiating internet & cable</h2>
        <p>Internet providers are notoriously competitive. Call and ask for the “customer retention” or “loyalty” department.</p>
        <div class="step-card">
            <span class="step-number">1</span> <strong>Check competitor rates</strong> – have a specific offer in mind (e.g., “AT&T is offering $50/month for the same speed”).
        </div>
        <div class="step-card">
            <span class="step-number">2</span> <strong>Call during business hours</strong> – weekday mornings are best.
        </div>
        <div class="step-card">
            <span class="step-number">3</span> <strong>Mention bundling</strong> – sometimes adding a service (like mobile) unlocks a discount.
        </div>
        <p>Typical outcome: a temporary promo or a permanent price reduction of $10–20/month.</p>

        <h2 id="phone"><i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i> Phone & wireless plans</h2>
        <p>Wireless carriers compete fiercely. Ask about loyalty discounts, employer discounts, or senior/military plans. If you own your phone, switch to a cheaper prepaid plan or an MVNO (like Mint, Visible).</p>
        <div class="highlight-box">
            <strong><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Sample line:</strong> “I’m thinking of switching to a prepaid plan to save money. Before I do, can you check if there’s a better postpaid plan or any discounts I’m missing?”
        </div>

        <h2 id="subscriptions"><i class="fas fa-clapperboard"></i> Subscriptions & memberships</h2>
        <p>Streaming services, gyms, magazines – many offer discounts if you try to cancel. Go to your account and click “cancel” – a retention offer often pops up. If not, call and say:</p>
        <div class="script-box">
            <i class="fas fa-quote-left"></i> “I love your service, but I’m cutting back on expenses. Do you have any promotional rate or annual plan that could make it more affordable?”
        </div>
        <p>For gyms, ask about seasonal deals or corporate discounts.</p>

        <h2 id="timing"><i class="fas fa-calendar-alt"></i> Best time to call</h2>
        <p>Timing can double your success rate:</p>
        <ul class="checklist">
            <li><i class="fas fa-calendar-day"></i> <strong>End of the month:</strong> Reps have quotas to meet.</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-clock"></i> <strong>Weekday mornings (Tue–Thu):</strong> shorter wait times, fresher reps.</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-tag"></i> <strong>Before a promo ends:</strong> If your discount is expiring, call a week before.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 id="apps"><i class="fas fa-robot"></i> Apps & tools that do the work for you</h2>
        <p>If you hate phone calls, try these:</p>
        <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 15px; margin: 20px 0;">
            <span class="badge">Billshark</span> <span> – negotiates for a cut of savings</span>
        </div>
        <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 15px; margin: 20px 0;">
            <span class="badge">Truebill / Rocket Money</span> <span> – cancels subscriptions and negotiates bills</span>
        </div>
        <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 15px; margin: 20px 0;">
            <span class="badge">Trim</span> <span> – similar service</span>
        </div>
        <p>Most charge 30–50% of first‑year savings, so it’s only worth it for big bills.</p>

        <h2 id="cheat-sheet"><i class="fas fa-scroll"></i> Negotiation cheat sheet</h2>
        <div style="background-color: #fefce8; border-radius: 20px; padding: 25px; margin: 30px 0;">
            <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">📋 Before you call, remember:</h3>
            <ul class="checklist">
                <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Be polite and friendly.</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Know what competitors charge.</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Ask for the retention department.</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Use the word “disconnect” or “cancel” only if you’re ready to follow through.</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> If one rep can’t help, hang up and call again (different rep, different outcome).</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Quick quiz -->
        {% if app.user and quiz %}
            {# Logged in user #}
            {# Quiz already taken – show summary and retake button #}
            <div class="quiz-container animate">
                <h3 style="color:white; margin-top: 0;">🧠 You've already taken this quiz</h3>
                <p style="color: #e2e8f0; font-size: 1.2rem;">
                    Your score: <strong>{{ quiz.quizzScore }}%</strong>
                </p>
                <p style="color: #cbd5e0;">
                    You can retake the quiz to improve your score. Click the button below to reset it.
                </p>
                <div class="quiz-actions">
                    <a href="{{ path('app_page_show', { journey: page.journey.name, slug: slug, retake: 1 }) }}"
                       class="btn"
                       style="background-color: #ff6b35; color: white; text-decoration: none;">
                        Retake Quiz
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        {% else %}
            {# Not logged in – show quiz (interactivity will be blocked by JS) #}
            <div class="quiz-container animate" data-page-id="{{ page.id }}">
                <h3 style="color:white; margin-top: 0;">🧠 Quick quiz: test your negotiation skills</h3>
                <div class="quiz-question">1. What percentage of people who ask for a better deal get one?</div>
                <div class="quiz-options" data-question="1">
                    <div class="quiz-option" data-answer="wrong">Around 25%</div>
                    <div class="quiz-option" data-answer="wrong">Around 50%</div>
                    <div class="quiz-option" data-answer="correct">Around 75%</div>
                    <div class="quiz-option" data-answer="wrong">Around 90%</div>
                </div>
                <div class="quiz-question">2. What is the best time to call to negotiate?</div>
                <div class="quiz-options" data-question="2">
                    <div class="quiz-option" data-answer="wrong">Weekend evenings</div>
                    <div class="quiz-option" data-answer="correct">Weekday mornings</div>
                    <div class="quiz-option" data-answer="wrong">Late night</div>
                    <div class="quiz-option" data-answer="wrong">During lunch hour</div>
                </div>
                <div class="quiz-question">3. Which department should you ask for?</div>
                <div class="quiz-options" data-question="3">
                    <div class="quiz-option" data-answer="wrong">Billing</div>
                    <div class="quiz-option" data-answer="wrong">Customer service</div>
                    <div class="quiz-option" data-answer="correct">Retention/loyalty</div>
                    <div class="quiz-option" data-answer="wrong">Technical support</div>
                </div>
                <div class="quiz-question">4. What should you have before calling?</div>
                <div class="quiz-options" data-question="4">
                    <div class="quiz-option" data-answer="wrong">Competitor offers</div>
                    <div class="quiz-option" data-answer="wrong">Your latest bill</div>
                    <div class="quiz-option" data-answer="wrong">A friendly attitude</div>
                    <div class="quiz-option" data-answer="correct">All of the above</div>
                </div>
                <div class="quiz-question">5. If a rep says no, what should you do?</div>
                <div class="quiz-options" data-question="5">
                    <div class="quiz-option" data-answer="correct">Hang up and call again</div>
                    <div class="quiz-option" data-answer="wrong">Yell at them</div>
                    <div class="quiz-option" data-answer="wrong">Give up</div>
                    <div class="quiz-option" data-answer="wrong">Switch immediately</div>
                </div>
                <div class="quiz-feedback">👉 Click any answer to check yourself.</div>
            </div>
        {% endif %}


        <!-- Next steps: continue Phase 3 -->
        <section style="margin: 60px 0;">
            <h2 class="section-title" style="text-align: center;">Continue your Practical Execution phase</h2>
            <div class="next-steps">
                <a href="{{ url('app_page_show', { journey: 'personal-finance', slug: 'opening-your-first-bank-account' }) }}" class="next-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-university" style="color: var(--personal-color);"></i>
                    <h3>Opening Your First Bank Account</h3>
                    <p style="color: var(--gray-color);">Step‑by‑step guide to choosing the right accounts, avoiding fees, and setting up direct deposits like a pro.</p>
                </a>
                <a href="{{ url('app_page_show', { journey: 'personal-finance', slug: 'automate-your-finances' }) }}" class="next-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-robot" style="color: var(--personal-color);"></i>
                    <h3>Automate Your Finances</h3>
                    <p style="color: var(--gray-color);">Walk through automating bill payments, savings transfers, and investments – the ultimate tool for consistency.</p>
                </a>
                <a href="{{ url('app_page_show', { journey: 'personal-finance', slug: 'creating-a-personal-financial-statement' }) }}" class="next-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-file-invoice" style="color: var(--personal-color);"></i>
                    <h3>Creating a Personal Financial Statement</h3>
                    <p style="color: var(--gray-color);">Track your net worth with a simple balance sheet and income statement. Know exactly where you stand.</p>
                </a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
{% endblock %}
